|CKBStreet Samurai Command Index|000

|CKBStatus and progression|000
|CK0dashboard - firmware version, Cortex, implant, strain, integrity, and alert diagnostic
samstatus - compact contract, progression, resource, and cycle report
samxp - Guild Level, Cortex Rank, banked GXP, and the next requirement
samspam [verbose|brief|off] - control implant activation message detail
gscore - shared progression display for all of your guilds
samskills - every routine, unlock, resource cost, and current readiness
monitor - automatic HP, SP, Edge, Heat, and active-process output
implants - all installed cyberware and other internal equipment
cyberware - internal locations, installed hardware, and strain capacity|000

|CKBNetwork|000
|CK0samwho - visible connected operators and pertinent guild state
samchat <message> - normal private Cortex transmission
samchat :<emote> - channel emote syntax
esamchat <message> - narrative channel syntax
samhist [lines] - recent private Cortex transmissions|000

|CKBMaintenance|000
|CK0defrag <process|all> - reduce firmware fragmentation
patch <process|all> - apply queued firmware updates
purge <process|all> - remove detected ICE intrusions
reboot <process|all> - clear registered runtime faults
logs [process] - review maintenance events for all or one process
samrepair - diagnose and recover a corrupt guild installation|000

|CKBFabrication|000
|CK0fabricate list - list Cortex fabrication blueprints
fabricate inspect <recipe> - inspect skill, guild level, and component costs
fabricate materials - show saved cybernetic components
fabricate <recipe> - build a repair kit at the fabrication table
salvage <hardware> - preview dismantling extracted cyberware
salvage <hardware> confirm - permanently dismantle the previewed hardware
repairkit <process_id> - consume a field kit to repair implant integrity|000

|CKBFirmware commands|000
|CK0neonwake, snapcut, jolt, overclock, threatscan, ripcut, armorweave,
photonlance, smartsmoke, ghoststep, traumabuffer, monowire, jammer, microswarm,
nanomend, predict, thermalpurge, zerosignal, and tempest.|000

|CK0Thermal Purge also accepts "vent" instead of a foe. This emergency mode
clears all Heat immediately but inflicts severe integrity wear on the Cortex OS
and Thermal Exchange Manifold.|000

|CKBPassive topics|000
|CK0samhelp cold signal - automatic thermal control
samhelp second spur - expanded Edge capacity and off-hand cutting support
samhelp overdrive - opening-burst Heat control
samhelp ronin-sama kernel - GL16 Cortex ascension and combat protocols|000

|CKBSystem topics|000
|CK0samhelp start - first-deployment checklist and first combat loop
samhelp contract - primary, secondary, inactive, and leaving states
samhelp progression - battle GXP, Guild Level, and Cortex Rank
samhelp resources - Edge, Heat, redline, cooling, and lockout
samhelp mon - monitor controls and process-indicator legend
samhelp firmware - requirements, interactions, and troubleshooting
samhelp hardware - grades, slots, strain, and loadout inspection
samhelp fabrication - salvage, Cybernetics, recipes, and repair kits
samhelp maintenance - integrity, fragmentation, alerts, and repairs
samhelp network - private chat, history, and samwho fields
samhelp prices - hardware purchases and procedure fees
samhelp leaving - consequences of ending membership|000

|CKBQuick diagnosis|000
|CK0If a routine fails, read its message. Then use samstatus for resources and
the Cortex cycle, samskills for unlocks and missing hardware, and dashboard for
implant condition or alerts. Use samhelp <command> for focused syntax and
operational guidance.|000
